<li>Persson, A., 1998 <i><a href="http://www.aos.princeton.edu/WWWPUBLIC/gkv/history/Persson98.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.aos.princeton.edu/WWWPUBLIC/gkv/history/Persson98.pdf" rel="nofollow">How do we Understand the Coriolis Force?</a></i> Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society 79, 1373–1385.</li>
<li>Symon, Keith. 1971, <i>Mechanics</i>, Addison-Wesley</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fi.edu/tfi/exhibits/bower/03/earth.html" class="external text" title="http://www.fi.edu/tfi/exhibits/bower/03/earth.html" rel="nofollow">Phillips, Norman A.</a>, 2000 <i><a href="http://www.met.utah.edu/reichler/6010/Coriolis/Phillips.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.met.utah.edu/reichler/6010/Coriolis/Phillips.pdf" rel="nofollow">An Explication of the Coriolis Effect</a></i>, Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society: Vol. 81, No. 2, pp. 299–303.</li>
