<li><a href="http://met.no/english/topics/nomek_2005/coriolis.pdf" class="external text" title="http://met.no/english/topics/nomek_2005/coriolis.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Coriolis Effect</a> PDF-file. 17 pages. A general discussion by Anders Persson of various aspects of the coriolis effect, including Foucault's Pendulum and Taylor columns.</li>
<li>Anders Persson <a href="http://www.meteohistory.org/2005historyofmeteorology2/01persson.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.meteohistory.org/2005historyofmeteorology2/01persson.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Coriolis Effect: Four centuries of conflict between common sense and mathematics, Part I: A history to 1885</a> History of Meteorology 2 (2005)</li>
