<li><a href="http://www.straightdope.com/classics/a1_161.html" class="external text" title="http://www.straightdope.com/classics/a1_161.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Do bathtubs drain counterclockwise in the Northern Hemisphere?</i></a> by Cecil Adams.</li>
